OL,3,CVietnam sentences real estate tycoon
OL,4,Cto death in nation's largest fraud case
OL,6,FReal estate tycoon Truong My Lan has
OL,7,Fbeen sentenced to death by a court in
OL,8,FHo Chi Minh city in southern Vietnam
OL,9,Fin the country's largest financial
OL,10,Ffraud case ever, state media Thanh
OL,11,FNien said.
OL,13,FThe 67-year-old chair of the real
OL,14,Festate company Van Thinh Phat was
OL,15,Fformally charged with fraud amounting
OL,16,Fto $12.5 billion (#9.9 billion) -
OL,17,Fnearly 3% of the country's 2022 GDP.
