OL,6,FLan illegally controlled Saigon Joint
OL,7,FStock Commercial Bank between 2012 and
OL,8,F2022 to allow 2,500 loans that
OL,9,Fresulted in losses of $27 billion
OL,10,F(#21.5 billion) to the bank, reported
OL,11,Fstate media VnExpress.
OL,13,FThe court asked her to compensate the
OL,14,Fbank $26.9 million (#21.4 million).
