OL,6,FHer actions "not only violate the
OL,7,Fproperty management rights of
OL,8,Findividuals and organisations but also
OL,9,Fpush SCB (Saigon Joint Stock
OL,10,FCommercial Bank) into a state of
OL,11,Fspecial control; eroding people's
OL,12,Ftrust in the leadership of the Party
OL,13,Fand State," VnExpress quoted the
OL,14,Fjudgement as saying.
OL,16,FThe 2011 merger of a beleaguered SCB
OL,17,Fbank involved two other lenders. The
OL,18,Fbanks have since become one of
OL,19,FVietnam's largest commercial banks by
OL,20,Fassets.
