OL,6,FFormer central bank official Do Thi
OL,7,FNhan was also sentenced Thursday to
OL,8,Flife in prison for accepting $5.2
OL,9,Fmillion in bribes.
OL,11,FLan's arrest in October 2022 was among
OL,12,Fthe most high-profile in an ongoing
OL,13,Fanti-corruption drive in Vietnam that
OL,14,Fhas intensified since 2022.
OL,16,FThe so-called Blazing Furnace campaign
OL,17,Fhas touched the highest echelons of
OL,18,FVietnamese politics. Former President
OL,19,FVo Van Thuong resigned in March after
OL,20,Fbeing implicated in the campaign.
